  "root_text": {
    "iti17:0.1": "Itivuttaka 17 ",
    "iti17:0.2": "Ekakanipāta ",
    "iti17:0.3": "Dutiyavagga ",
    "iti17:0.4": "Dutiyasekhasutta ",
    "iti17:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti17:2.1": "“Sekhassa, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno appattamānasassa anuttaraṁ yogakkhemaṁ patthayamānassa viharato bāhiraṁ aṅganti karitvā nāññaṁ ekaṅgampi samanupassāmi yaṁ evaṁ bahūpakāraṁ yathayidaṁ, bhikkhave, kalyāṇamittatā. ",
    "iti17:2.2": "Kalyāṇamitto, bhikkhave, bhikkhu akusalaṁ pajahati, kusalaṁ bhāvetī”ti. ",
    "iti17:2.3": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti17:2.4": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti17:3.1": "“Kalyāṇamitto yo bhikkhu, ",
    "iti17:3.2": "sappatisso sagāravo; ",
    "iti17:3.3": "Karaṁ mittānaṁ vacanaṁ, ",
    "iti17:3.4": "sampajāno patissato; ",
    "iti17:3.5": "Pāpuṇe anupubbena, ",
    "iti17:3.6": "sabbasaṁyojanakkhayan”ti. ",
    "iti17:4.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti17:4.2": "Sattamaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti17:0.1": "So It Was Said 17 ",
    "iti17:0.2": "The Book of the Ones ",
    "iti17:0.3": "Chapter Two ",
    "iti17:0.4": "A Trainee (2nd) ",
    "iti17:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti17:2.1": "“Taking into account exterior factors, mendicants, I do not see a single one that is so very helpful as good friendship for a trainee mendicant who hasn’t achieved their heart’s desire, but lives aspiring to the supreme sanctuary from the yoke. ",
    "iti17:2.2": "A mendicant who has good friends gives up the unskillful and develops the skillful.” ",
    "iti17:2.3": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti17:2.4": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti17:3.1": "“A mendicant with good friends ",
    "iti17:3.2": "is reverential and respectful ",
    "iti17:3.3": "when their friends are speaking, ",
    "iti17:3.4": "aware and mindful. ",
    "iti17:3.5": "Gradually they would attain ",
    "iti17:3.6": "the ending of all fetters.” ",
    "iti17:4.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
